What's Covered?

Lemonade covers your belongings both at home and everywhere else.

Personal Property

Clothes, electronics, furniture, and everything else you own

Liability

Protection if someone gets hurt in your place or you damage their stuff

Additional Living

Hotel costs if your place becomes unlivable

Medical Payments

Medical bills if a guest gets injured at your place

Starting at $5/month

Most people pay around $12-15/month for comprehensive renters insurance. Coverage starting at $5/month is available for basic personal property protection.

$12
per month (average)
  • $30K personal property
  • $100K liability
  • $5K additional living
  • Worldwide coverage

Get Covered in 3 Steps

1

Tell us about yourself

Answer a few questions about your living situation and belongings.

2

Get instant quote

See your price and coverage options in real-time.

3

You're covered

Purchase your policy and get your documents instantly.
